      "review_summary": "The PR adds a Feishu `extractEmojiOnly()` helper and applies it to outbound payload cards, renderMode card sends, and reply-dispatcher card headers built from `identity.emoji`.\n\nPR surface: Source +21. Total +21 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level. Current main concatenates raw `identity.emoji` into Feishu card header titles in outbound and reply-dispatcher paths; I did not run a live Feishu send in this read-only review.",
